{{otheruses4|the dwarven bartender|the gnomish adventurer|Popkin Shortshanks}}
'''Shortshanks''' was a [[dwarf]] and the owner of the [[Bold Bard]] tavern in the town of [[Ghars]] in [[Cormyr]] in the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
{{quote|Well, I'm not a warrior, am I, Mister War Wizard Smarty-Pants? I'm a barkeep, in case you haven't noticed. Come down out of your ivory tower and drop by, and I'll give ye an [[ale]], if you're man enough to handle it.|Shortshanks}}
